sequenceDiagram
  participant Customer
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as NestJS API
  participant Agent as Deployment Agent
  participant Queue as Redis Queue
  participant Deploy as Deploy Worker
  participant Netlify
  participant Verify as Verification Worker
  participant DB as Postgres

  Customer->>FE: Approve page version
  FE->>API: create release plan
  API->>Agent: run preflight
  Agent->>DB: read approvals, notes, routes, SEO data
  Agent->>DB: save checks and release plan
  API-->>FE: release ready / blocked / warnings
  Customer->>FE: Approve deploy
  FE->>API: approve release deploy
  API->>Queue: deploy_worker.execute_release
  Queue->>Deploy: start release deployment
  Deploy->>Netlify: build and deploy
  Netlify-->>Deploy: deploy result
  Deploy->>DB: save deployment
  Deploy->>Queue: verification_worker.verify_release
  Queue->>Verify: verify live URLs
  Verify->>DB: save verification results
  API-->>FE: live status and release notes
